<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:09:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列陷入战争，第 194 天：真主党在无人机和导弹袭击以色列北部的情况下造成至少 18 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-194-hezbollah-wounds-at-least-18-in-missile-attack-on-north-israel/0000018e-ed03-dbb3-a3bf-fdcf89fe0000</link><description>以色列北部真主党火箭弹袭击造成至少 18 人受伤 ■ 美国官员预计以色列将在伊朗领土上进行“有限打击”以回应伊朗袭击 ■ 英国外长：明确表示以色列打算对伊朗袭击作出回应 ■ 伊朗：军方已做好应对任何袭击的准备以色列对袭击“做出严厉回应” ■ 卡塔尔总理：停火谈判正处于“微妙阶段” ■ 战争已过去 194 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-194-hezbollah-wounds-at-least-18-in-missile-attack-on-north-israel/0000018e-ed03-dbb3-a3bf-fdcf89fe0000</guid></item><item><title>对于 10 月 7 日逃离哈马斯的以色列人来说，高速公路变成了死亡陷阱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</link><description>因巴尔开车去打架，尽管他的女朋友恳求他不要这么做。莎妮设法与她的祖父进行了最后一次视频通话。他们只是加沙边境附近道路上无法躲避哈马斯的 250 多人中的两人</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:34:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役人员情况危急，四人在无人机和导弹对北部的袭击中受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-in-critical-condition-4-seriously-wounded-in-drone-rocket-attack-on-north/0000018e-ec8c-daad-a3de-eebfd45c0000</link><description>一架无人机和反坦克导弹袭击以色列北部阿拉伯阿拉姆谢的建筑物