0000018e-eb79-d35c-a39e-fb7b15160000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列和美国结盟打击伊朗的阿拉伯国家现在面临后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-allied-with-israel-and-u-s-for-iran-attack-now-face-consequences/0000018e-eb42-d35c-a39e-fb6318100000</link><description>阿拉伯国家深知，只有以色列是伊朗的瞄准目标，而且其利益没有受到直接威胁，鉴于加沙攻势，阿拉伯国家现在面临着向公众解释其前所未有的联盟的困难</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-allied-with-israel-and-u-s-for-iran-attack-now-face-consequences/0000018e-eb42-d35c-a39e-fb6318100000</guid></item><item><title>英国和德国高级外交官抵达以色列，以缓和其对伊朗的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/british-german-top-diplomats-arrive-in-israel-in-bid-to-temper-its-reaction-to-iran/0000018e-eaef-d35c-a39e-fbef70610000</link><description>卡梅伦和贝尔博克将与几位以色列高级政府官员会面，并警告他们不要进一步升级与德黑兰的紧张局势，此前他们的国家协助以色列挫败了大规模袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/british-german-top-diplomats-arrive-in-israel-in-bid-to-temper-its-reaction-to-iran/0000018e-eaef-d35c-a39e-fbef70610000</guid></item><item><title>耶稣最后的晚餐真的是逾越节家宴吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/was-jesus-last-supper-truly-a-passover-seder/0000018e-eaaa-d35c-a39e-fbeb130d0000</link><description>耶稣祝福了面包还是无酵饼？福音书提供了相互矛盾的答案，引发了圣经之谜</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:22:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/was-jesus-last-supper-truly-a-passover-seder/0000018e-eaaa-d35c-a39e-fbeb130d0000</guid></item><item><title>“和平运动失败了”：为什么这位美国福音派人士想要停止武装以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-peace-movement-has-failed-why-this-u-s-evangelical-wants-to-stop-arming-israel/0000018e-e740-db8e-a1bf-ff4f7d080000</link><description>中东和平教会执行主任梅·埃莉斯·坎农牧师博士日益成为美国福音派社区中以色列最大的批评者之一。她解释了为什么本月无法庆祝其联盟成立 40 周年</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:37:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-peace-movement-has-failed-why-this-u-s-evangelical-wants-to-stop-arming-israel/0000018e-e740-db8e-a1bf-ff4f7d080000</guid></item><item><title>未能预见德黑兰的战略转变后，以色列必须谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-tread-carefully-after-failing-to-foresee-tehrans-change-of-strategy/0000018e-e889-d7e3-a9bf-fcbd95670000</link><description>伊朗的导弹和无人机袭击失败了，但以色列高级官员却因回应而陷入困境——回应的时间和性质将由加沙和美国的立场决定。 ■ 地区战争将危及伊朗即将发生的权力交接</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-tread-carefully-after-failing-to-foresee-tehrans-change-of-strategy/0000018e-e889-d7e3-a9bf-fcbd95670000</guid></item><item><title>由于家人警告伊朗局势升级，外国外交官寻求释放以色列人质的新途径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/warning-that-situation-is-bleak-diplomats-seek-new-path-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018e-e889-d0ca-a99f-fdfbfb100000</link><description>接近会谈的消息人士称，美国最新的提议不够有创意，未能弥合哈马斯和以色列要求之间的差距</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 03:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/warning-that-situation-is-bleak-diplomats-seek-new-path-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018e-e889-d0ca-a99f-fdfbfb100000</guid></item><item><title>火箭弹和无人机袭击以色列北部后，五名以色列国防军预备役人员伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-live/u-s-plans-new-iran-sanctions-israeli-war-cabinet-to-discuss-response-to-missile-attack/0000018e-e9b3-dba7-a3ee-fdfb68870000</link><description>包括 13 名预备役军人在内的 18 人在阿拉伯阿拉姆谢地区受伤 ■ 德国、英国外长在以色列敦促以色列缓和对伊朗的反应 ■ 英国外交大臣称以色列“正在做出采取行动的决定” ■ 报告：美国预计以色列将采取行动在伊朗进行“有限打击” 据