nal-cooperation-that-thwarted-the-iranian-attack-came-together/0000018e-e7a6-d7e3-a9bf-f7b709160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人和伊朗人似乎在一件事上达成了共识：我们谁都不想要这场战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-16/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-and-iranians-seem-to-agree-on-one-thing-none-of-us-want-this-war/0000018e-e739-db5b-afbe-ffbb39f50000</link><description>对我们来说不幸的是，伊朗和以色列的领导者将贪婪、骄傲和敌意置于人民之上——尽管两国开展了大规模抗议活动以结束这种情况</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:52:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-16/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-and-iranians-seem-to-agree-on-one-thing-none-of-us-want-this-war/0000018e-e739-db5b-afbe-ffbb39f50000</guid></item></channel></rss>